# Paraglide v2 generated runtime (#7.6). Regenerated on every
# `vite dev` / `vite build` from `project.inlang/settings.json`
# + `messages/*.json`; checking it in would just produce noisy
# diffs and stale-runtime confusion when somebody edits a
# message without re-running compile.
/src/lib/paraglide

# inlang-managed files inside `project.inlang/`. `settings.json`
# is hand-edited and tracked; `.meta.json` + `README.md` are
# vendored by the tool on every paraglide compile and would
# otherwise leave a dirty tree after each run.
/project.inlang/.meta.json
/project.inlang/README.md

